5.body: A list of components that can be used. A GameObject can hold up to 32 components, but not have multiple RenderComponents. A TransformComponent used for moving actors around the scene. These are created by the engine within the CreateEntity() function. Each GameObject has a GetTransform() which returns the TransformComponent. A RenderComponent used rendering objects to the screen.
